Node "Mich_2_3a_2b_2b_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Crossroads is a small but thriving settlement built around an old, pre-war farm, where several caravan runs cross one another, hence the name. In another lifetime, I was very much part of it's... ribald and colorful community."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "'In another lifetime?' Do you believe in reincarnation or something?" linkto "Mich_2_3a_2b_2b_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You mentioned before that you worked there. What did you do?" linkto "Mich_3_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Could you tell me how to find Crossroads?" linkto "Mich_2_3a_2b_2a_2b_1"  notes ""
