Node "Mich_2_3a_2b_2c_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "This is a sickly place, my son. I hope for your sake that you are carrying enough of the right medicines to cope with the background radiation which blights our lives."
 NPCFemaleText "This is a sickly place, my child. I hope for your sake that you are carrying enough of the right medicines to cope with the background radiation which blights our lives."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "If Sandover is so heavily contaminated, why do people stay here?" linkto "Mich_2_3a_2b_2c_2a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "If Sandover is so contaminated, why are you here?" linkto "Mich_2_3a_2b_2c_2b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Which parts of the wastes are you familiar with?" linkto "Mich_2_3a_2b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have a question for you about something else." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_2_3a_2b_2c_2a_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "The people of Sandover have nowhere else to go. Most of the Wasteland is less radioactive than the land around Sandover, but none of it is so rich with valuable pre-war technology. Scavenging for this technology is what provides Sandover with a source of income."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Whether or not there is money to be made here, why do people stay when the risk to their lives is so great?" linkto "Mich_2_3a_2b_2c_2a_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "If Sandover is so contaminated, why are you here?" linkto "Mich_2_3a_2b_2c_2b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Which parts of the wastes are you familiar with?" linkto "Mich_2_3a_2b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have a question for you about something else." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_2_3a_2b_2c_2a_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Most of the people here are outcasts, my son. Some are criminals; some were exiled because they refused to fit in with the societies into which they were born; some are deformed and were driven out by the intolerance shown to them. It is not for nothing that other wastelanders unkindly call the people of Sandover 'Scabs'."
 NPCFemaleText "Most of the people here are outcasts, my child. Some are criminals; some were exiled because they refused to fit in with the societies into which they were born; some are deformed and were driven out by the intolerance shown to them. It is not for nothing that other wastelanders unkindly call the people of Sandover 'Scabs'."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So why are you here?" linkto "Mich_2_3a_2b_2c_2b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Which parts of the wastes are you familiar with?" linkto "Mich_2_3a_2b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have a question for you about something else." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_2_3a_2b_2c_2b_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I am here because the people of Sandover need me. I consider myself blessed that I am able to give them some comfort where all others may disregard them."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why help the people here, where it is so dangerous, and not somewhere else?" linkto "Mich_2_3a_2b_2c_2b_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "If Sandover is so heavily contaminated, why do people stay here?" linkto "Mich_2_3a_2b_2c_2a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about what you do around Sandover." linkto "Mich_2_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Which parts of the wastes are you familiar with?" linkto "Mich_2_3a_2b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have a question for you about something else." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
              }
}
