Node "Mich_2_3a_2d_2b"
notes "Increment the variable Mich_Rude by 1."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "No, I don't 'get tired' of what I do and what I am. You're not going to last long in the wastes with a flippant attitude such as yours, young man."
 NPCFemaleText "No, I don't 'get tired' of what I do and what I am. You're not going to last long in the wastes with a flippant attitude such as yours, young lady."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You're right. I would like to hear your advice about something genuinely important." linkto "Mich_2_3a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I take it back. Remind me what those things you do in Sandover are." linkto "Mich_2_2"  notes ""
