notes "Increment Mich_Danger_Site by 1."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Very well. It is rare to meet someone who could cope in such extreme conditions, but you have the look of one who could. I used to be a good judge of these things. Do bear in mind, though, that this is an area of massively high radiation. It will test your resources to their very limits."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Where can I find it?" linkto "Mich_3_4_3"  notes ""
              }
}
