}
Node "Mich_5_1"
notes "The Mich_5_* path is where the PC learns that Michael is one of the Wasteland Explorers Bruce thinks died during the Sandover expedition. The PC also finds out that three of the bones sets are still at the expedition site and that Michael knows where the other two are. Michael demands that the PC finds the three bones sets and counter before showing him the last two sets (at the cemetary)."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "The Wasteland Explorers, yes, that's right. I suppose you've met them?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have. Do you know Bruce?" linkto "Mich_5_2a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have. Do you know Miranda?" linkto "Mich_5_2b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have a question I need to ask you about something else." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_5_2a"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Bruce! Of course I remember that old rogue. He and I were born in Rusty Springs and grew up together, you know."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "He would like the bodies of the people he lost during the Sandover expedition brought back to Crossroads for burial." linkto "Mich_5_3"  notes "This node only appears if the PC has accepted the bones quest from Bruce, the Explorer Representitive."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What can you tell me about Rusty Springs?" linkto "Mich_2_3a_2b_2a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Interesting. I have a question I need to ask you about something else." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_5_2b"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Miranda... no. I assume because you mention her that she's with the Explorers now. She must have joined since I left."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "She's Bruce's wife. Do you know him?" linkto "Mich_5_2a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have a question I need to ask you about something else." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_5_3"
notes "Make the variable Mich_Bones_Know=1"
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "*Michael's mood darkens.* Does he, now? So he thinks to rescue his team-mates now that they're so many bleached bones lying in the sun. What good will that do them?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Do you know where the bones are?" linkto "Mich_5_4"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Perhaps I'd better ask you about something else." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe I should leave." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_5_4"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Yes, I know exactly where some of them are, and I know where to look for the others. That does not mean I should do Bruce a favour by telling you about them, though."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm not sure I follow you." linkto "Mich_5_5"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Perhaps I'd better ask you about something else." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe I should leave." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_5_5"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Then let me explain. On the day our companions died, when we realised how radioactive the site was, Bruce was more concerned with carrying away the tech we'd found than getting our sick away from the site. He is not the man who should honor them now that they are dead."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "His greed sickens me. I've decided I'm not going to bring him the bones, after all." linkto "Mich_5_6c_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm just here to pick the bones up. I don't care about the reasons." linkto "Mich_5_6a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "He explained to me that he knew at the time that the Explorers who died were doomed. I think he did the right thing in making sure he had enough of a find to make the trip worthwhile." linkto "Mich_5_6b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Perhaps I'd better ask you about something else." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe I should leave." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_5_6a_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I see. No doubt Bruce has offered to pay you in some way. Well, perhaps I can help you, but only if you prove that your motives are not just material gain at Bruce's expense."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What do you mean?" linkto "Mich_5_6a_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Just tell me where the damn bones are so I won't have to hurt you." linkto "Mich_5_7_B_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Perhaps I'd better ask you about something else." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "We should talk about this another time. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_5_6a_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Remember that the bones we're talking about once belonged to people who were my friends. I'm not so easily going to turn them over to someone who only wants them so he can make a few caps."
 NPCFemaleText "Remember that the bones we're talking about once belonged to people who were my friends. I'm not so easily going to turn them over to someone who only wants them so she can make a few caps."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What do you want in return for letting me know how to get the bones?" linkto "Mich_5_7_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me where to find the bones are now, or I'll break some of yours." linkto "Mich_5_7_B_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Perhaps I'd better ask you about something else." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I think I ought to leave before I hear this." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_5_6b_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Perhaps you are right. I have always known Bruce to be a basically decent person. Greedy, but decent otherwise. As more time has passed since that dreadful day, I have been increasingly doubtful whether his motives were as callous as I once thought they were."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Could you please tell me how to find the bones?" linkto "Mich_5_6b_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Perhaps I'd better ask you about something else." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe I should leave." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_5_6b_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Maybe... yes. However, although you strike me as someone who understands how painful the memory of the expedition disaster is for those of us who survived it, I have to consider that your motivation is possibly only material gain at Bruce's expense."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- MORE -" linkto "Mich_5_6a_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Is that such a bad thing?" linkto "Mich_5_6b_3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Perhaps I'd better ask you about something else." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to go." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_5_6b_3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Ah. My suspicions are confirmed. Very well, bounty hunter, I shall give you the chance to win your 'prize'. However, you shall have to earn the knowledge of the bones' whereabouts, first."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Earn it? How? Why?" linkto "Mich_5_6a_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How about I repeatedly punch you in the face until you decide to tell me where they are?" linkto "Mich_5_7_B_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Perhaps I'd better ask you about something else." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe I should leave." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_5_6c_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Hmm... although I say this against my better judgement, maybe you are being too hasty. In many ways, it made sense that Bruce chose to take the items he found instead of the dying. It could be that he even knew that they were doomed."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No. My mind is made up. I can't believe Bruce even talked me into coming here." linkto "Mich_5_6c_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Actually, that's exactly what he said to me. Perhaps he did the right thing in making sure he had enough of a find to make the trip worthwhile." linkto "Mich_5_6b_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Perhaps I'd better ask you about something else." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- LEAVE -" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_5_6c_2"
notes "This ends the bones quest early without resolution. The player option in the node Mich_5_2a which reads, \"He would like the bodies of the people he lost during the Sandover expedition brought back to Crossroads for burial.\" will no longer appear."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "As you wish. It is probably for the best that the bones are left in peace where they lie."
      options {
