Node "Mich_5_7_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "The other two sets are somewhere safe. I shall tell you how to find them once you show me the three sets from the expedition site. There is one more condition, though."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Wait, Bruce told me that six Explorers died during the expedition." linkto "Mich_5_7_3a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let's hear it." linkto "Mich_5_7_3b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Perhaps I'd better ask you about something else." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I think I ought to leave before I hear this." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_5_7_3a"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I see. He probably thinks I died, too. I am the sixth member of the team that did not return with him to Crossroads. However, Bruce cannot have my bones until I am through using them!"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So there are only five sets of bones to find?" linkto "Mich_5_7_3b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Perhaps I'd better ask you about something else." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I think I ought to leave." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_5_7_3b"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I also want you to find a geiger counter, which I lost somewhere whilst we at the site. It will be hard to find; I remember spending most of the short time we were there looking for it. You will be able to find it in the same area where the bones lie, though."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Fine. Anything else?" linkto "Mich_5_7_4a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I could trade for a new one somewhere a lot less dangerous." linkto "Mich_5_7_4b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Wait a minute. YOU lost the geiger counter?" linkto "Mich_B_1" conditions { CHECK_STAT intelligence >= 6 link_next NONE } notes "IF the variable Mich_Guilt_Trip>0 (which means that the PC has already tried the guilt trip and failed), then go to Mich_B_0 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else, to give me time to think about this." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_5_7_4a_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "No, that's it. If you haven't gathered it already, stranger, this area is extremely radioactive, so if you are brave enough to go there, make sure you have plenty of protection from the rads."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You'll need to tell me where to find the expedition site." linkto "Mich_5_7_4a_2a"  notes "IF Mich_Danger_Site >= 1 then go to Mich_5_7_4a_2b instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else, to give me time to think about this." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye. I'll speak to you again soon." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_5_7_4a_2a"
notes "Add the location of the extremely high rad site to the PC's worldmap. Increment the variable Mich_Danger_Site by 1."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Ah, of course. Here, let me show you. *Michael uses some small ornaments to demonstrate landmarks that will help you find the site.* Here, it's just West of Sandover."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else, whilst I'm here." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll be back when I've found what you want. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_5_7_4a_2b"
notes "I'll be back when I've found the bones and your geiger counter. Goodbye."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I have already told you where it is, my son."
 NPCFemaleText "I have already told you where it is, my child."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else, to give me time to think about this." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "It sounds too dangerous. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_5_7_4b_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I don't doubt it. However, the geiger counter at the expedition site has a certain... symbolic significance. It would mean a great deal to me if you were to find it and bring it here."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Do you want anything else, other than the bones and the geiger counter?" linkto "Mich_5_7_4a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What do you mean by 'symbolic significance'?" linkto "Mich_5_7_4b_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What's to stop me from bringing back any old geiger counter? " linkto "Mich_5_7_4b_2b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Was this geiger counter you lost the only one the group had?" linkto "Mich_B_1"  notes "IF the variable Mich_Guilt_Trip>0 (which means that the PC has already tried the guilt trip and failed), then go to Mich_B_0 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else, to give me time to think about this." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_5_7_4b_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "*Michael pauses and shakes his head in shame.* The geiger counter I lost was the only one the group had. Without another, we had no way of telling how dangerous the site was. To be able to hold it in my hands again would, perhaps, help me face my... failure, and put the events of that day behind me."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Do you want anything else, other than the bones and the geiger counter?" linkto "Mich_5_7_4a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What's to stop me from bringing back any old geiger counter? " linkto "Mich_5_7_4b_2b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That means YOU are solely responsible for the deaths of your companions!" linkto "Mich_B_2"  notes "IF the variable Mich_Guilt_Trip>0 (which means that the PC has already tried the guilt trip and failed), then go to Mich_B_0 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else, to give me time to think about this." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_5_7_4b_2b_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I carved my initials into the counter's casing: M.S."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Do you want anything else, other than the bones and the geiger counter?" linkto "Mich_5_7_4a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What is the significance of this geiger counter over any other?" linkto "Mich_5_7_4b_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What does the 'S' stand for?" linkto "Mich_5_7_4b_2b_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Was this geiger counter you lost the only one the group had?" linkto "Mich_B_1"  notes "IF the variable Mich_Guilt_Trip>0 (which means that the PC has already tried the guilt trip and failed), then go to Mich_B_0 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else, to give me time to think about this." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_5_7_4b_2b_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Seymour. It's my last name."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Do you want anything else, other than the bones and the geiger counter?" linkto "Mich_5_7_4a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why does this geiger counter have 'symbolic significance'?" linkto "Mich_5_7_4b_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Was this geiger counter you lost the only one the group had?" linkto "Mich_B_1"  notes "IF the variable Mich_Guilt_Trip>0 (which means that the PC has already tried the guilt trip and failed), then go to Mich_B_0 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else, to give me time to think about this." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_5_7_B_1"
notes "Make the variable Mich_Rude=1"
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Huh! Do your worst, if you think it will help. I shall not betray my friends' resting place; especially to an animal like you."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Okay, what do you want in return for letting me know how to get the bones?" linkto "Mich_5_7_B_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- FIGHT -" linkto "combat"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_5_7_B_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Forget it, stranger. You've shown me enough of yourself for me to know that you would not honor the memories of my friends."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me where the bones are or I'll kill you." linkto "Mich_5_7_B_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Would you mind at least answering a question I have for you?" linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Then we have nothing more to say to each other. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_6_1"
notes "The Mich_6_* path is where the PC brings the bones and/or geiger counter from the Sandover expedition site to show to Michael so that the Priest will let the PC dig up the bones at Sandover's cemetary."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Have you managed to find anything yet, my son?"
 NPCFemaleText "Have you managed to find anything yet, my child?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I found this geiger counter. I think it's yours." linkto "Mich_6_2a"  notes "This node only appears if the PC has found the geiger counter marked with the initials M.S. AND Mich_G_Counter_Return=0."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I found these bones. Do you think you could tell if they belonged to a companion of yours?" linkto "Mich_6_2b"  notes "This node only appears if the PC has found at least one set of the Explorers' bones at the high-rad expedition site. Perhaps we need a different variable for each set of bones at the expedition site, so the script knows which set of bones has been checked by Michael or not."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm not sure where to look for the bones. Please tell me where to find the site." linkto "Mich_5_7_4a_2a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No, not yet. Let me ask you about something else." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_6_2a"
notes "Increment Mich_G_Counter_Return by 1."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Yes! This is it! This is it! Thank you, my son. You have no idea what this means to me."
 NPCFemaleText "Yes! This is it! This is it! Thank you, my child. You have no idea what this means to me."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That's the three sets of bones and one geiger counter. Does this mean you will tell me where the last two sets of bones are?" linkto "Mich_6_3"  notes "This node only appears IF Mich_G_Counter_Return>=1 AND Mich_Site_Bones_Return=3."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I found these bones. Do you think you could tell if they belonged to a companion of yours?" linkto "Mich_6_2b"  notes "This node only appears if the PC has found at least one set of the Explorers' bones at the high-rad expedition site. Perhaps we need a different variable for each set of bones at the expedition site, so the script knows which set of bones has been checked by Michael or not."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No, not yet. Let me ask you about something else." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_6_2b"
notes "Increment Mich_Site_Bones_Return by 1 for each new set of bones the PC shows to Michael."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Let me see... *He looks closely at the bones.* Oh my, yes. It's amazing how you can still recognize someone by looking at their skull. Poor souls."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That's the three sets of bones and one geiger counter. Does this mean you will tell me where the last two sets of bones are?" linkto "Mich_6_3"  notes "This node only appears IF Mich_G_Counter_Return>=1 AND Mich_Site_Bones_Return=3."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I also found this geiger counter. I think it's yours." linkto "Mich_6_2a"  notes "This node only appears if the PC has found the geiger counter marked with the initials M.S. AND Mich_G_Counter_Return=0."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_6_3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Yes, you have earned that much, my son. The bones of the final two Explorers are in our cemetary. You will need a shovel in order to dig them up."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "As it happens, I have a shovel. Lead the way." linkto "Mich_6_4a_1"  notes "This node only appears IF the PC has a shovel in his inventory."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I don't have a shovel. Do you have one I could borrow?" linkto "Mich_6_4b"  notes "This node only appears IF the PC does not have a shovel in his inventory."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else, first." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I don't have time to go digging. Goodbye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_6_4a_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Follow me. I'll lead you to the cemetary."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- MORE -" linkto "Mich_6_4a_2"  notes "The screen fades to black; a few hours pass; screen fades back; PC has all the bones."
              }
}
Node "Mich_6_4a_2"
notes "Decrement Mich_Rude by 2. Make Mich_Shovel=0. Make Mich_Alex_Force=0. Increment Mich_Cemetary_Bones by 2. Put the bones of the two Explorers buried in the Sandover cemetary in the PC's inventory."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "*You return to Michael's room after several hours of heavy, dusty digging. You now have the bones of the two Explorers who were buried in Sandover's cemetary. The priest looks at you in concern.* That looked like hard work. Would you like a drink?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Yes, please. What do you have?" linkto "Mich_6_4a_3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No, thanks. I had better leave." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have a question I'd like to ask you instead." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_6_4a_3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Just water, I'm afraid. I don't keep alcohol."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Water sounds just fine." linkto "Mich_6_4a_4b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That sounds good. No offense, but with this being Sandover, I presume it's safe to drink?" linkto "Mich_6_4a_4a" conditions { CHECK_SKILL outdoorsman >= 50 link_next NONE } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Actually, I have a question I'd like to ask you instead." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No, thanks. I want a drink, not a wash. I had better leave." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_6_4a_4a"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Of course. All our drinking water is from Rusty Springs and it all gets drunk before the background radiation has a chance to contaminate it."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "In that case, water sounds just fine." linkto "Mich_6_4a_4b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have a question I'd like to ask you instead." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I think I'll leave it, thanks all the same. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_6_4a_4b"
notes "Maybe some sort of tiny health boost at this point because of the drink?"
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Here, take this. *Michael hands you an earthenware mug filled with water, which you drink in one draught. You are surprised by how thirsty you are. When you are finished, you hand the mug back to the priest.* What will you do now, my son?"
 NPCFemaleText "Here, take this. *Michael hands you an earthenware mug filled with water, which you drink in one draught. You are surprised by how thirsty you are. When you are finished, you hand the mug back to the priest.* What will you do now, my child?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Would you like to come to Crossroads to preside over the burial of the Explorers' bones?" linkto "Mich_8a_1"  notes "This option only appears if the variable Mich_Site_Bones_Return=3 AND Mich_Cemetary_Bones=2. \nIF Mich_G_Counter_Return<=0, go to Mich_8b_1 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have a question I'd like to ask you." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'd better be going. Goodbye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_6_4b"
notes "Increment Mich_Shovel by 1."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "No. I am not one for material possessions, my son. You will need to find a shovel from elsewhere. Your Explorer friends will doubtless have one."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else before I go off to find the shovel." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Hopefully I'll be able to find one in Sandover. Goodbye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll have to go back to Crossroads, then. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_7_1"
notes "The Mich_7_* path is for the condition of the bones quest where the PC has convinced the Scab leader, Alexander, to overrule Michael. This allows the PC to force Michael to take him to the two sets of bones buried in Sandover's cemetary."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Alexander said that?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "He did. Tell me where the two sets of bones you know about are and how I can get them." linkto "Mich_7_2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_7_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Give me a moment. I should like to check this with Alexander myself."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll be waiting here." linkto "Mich_7_3"  notes "Fade the screen to black and back again to simulate the time it takes for Michael to go to Alexander to confirm his overruling and come back again. If possible, make five minutes pass."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Don't keep me waiting too long." linkto "Mich_7_3"  notes "Fade the screen to black and back again to simulate the time it takes for Michael to go to Alexander to confirm his overruling and come back again. If possible, make five minutes pass."
              }
}
Node "Mich_7_3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "*Michael returns to his room. He looks awkward; you can imagine the heated words that he and Alexander exchanged.* It appears I owe you an apology, stranger. Alexander did indeed give you his blessing. If you want to collect the bones now, they're in our cemetary; you'll need a shovel so you can dig them up."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No time like the present. Let's go." linkto "Mich_6_4a_1"  notes "This node only appears if the PC has a shovel in his inventory."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I don't have a shovel. Do you have one I could borrow?" linkto "Mich_6_4b"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_8a_1"
notes "The Mich_8_* path is where the PC can invite Michael back to Crossroads in order to preside over the burial of the five dead Explorers. The PC needs to have found and returned the geiger counter to Michael, as well as gathered the five bones set in order to do this."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "*Michael is taken aback by your suggestion.* That is a truly noble gesture on your part, my son. I would be honored to help in any way I can with the ceremony."
 NPCFemaleText " *Michael is taken aback by your suggestion.* That is a truly noble gesture on your part, my child. I would be honored to help in any way I can with the ceremony."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- MORE -" linkto "Mich_8a_2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_8a_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "*The priest becomes more emotional as he speaks.* This... really means a lot to me, you know. To be able to make my peace with Bruce and the others in the group would be... very helpful. *He pauses and breathes heavily.* I'm sorry... it's just..."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Don't worry, I think I understand." linkto "Mich_8a_3"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_8a_3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "*Michael gathers his thoughts.* So how shall we arrange this?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Leave for Crossroads as soon as you can. Wait for me to talk to Bruce and we'll take it from there." linkto "Mich_8a_4"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_8a_4"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Very well. I'll pack what few things I'll need for the journey and be on my way. Will you be coming soon?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Yes, I think I'm finished in Sandover. Goodbye for now; I'll see you at Crossroads." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No, there are still some things I have to do before I go back to Crossroads. I'll leave you to your packing." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_8b_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "*Michael considers your suggestion for a few moments.* No... I don't think that would be appropriate, my son. There are still many ghosts to be laid to rest in my relationship with the Explorers for me to return to Crossroads and face them."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How could I help you to put these ghosts to rest?" linkto "Mich_8b_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Never mind. Let me ask you another question in that case." linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I had better leave." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_8b_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Well, the image that keeps appearing in my mind whenever I think of the Sandover expedition is of the geiger counter I lost. If you were to find that, I could take the first, and perhaps the most difficult step, in coming to terms with my part in the disaster."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I've forgotten where you said the geiger counter could be found. Please remind me." linkto "Mich_8b_3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Was the geiger counter you lost the only one your group had?" linkto "Mich_B_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I had better leave." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_8b_3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "If the geiger counter still hasn't been found, it'll be lying out at the expedition site. I'm afraid you'll need to return to that area again if you are going to find it."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "*Put in a link to the geiger guilt trip.*" linkto "Mich_0"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I remember, now. Could I ask you a question about something else?" linkto "Mich_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll go and find it now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Mich_9"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "What do you wish to know?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What do you do in Sandover?" linkto "Mich_2_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Have you lived in Sandover all your life?" linkto "Mich_4_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What can you tell me about Sandover?" linkto "Mich_2_3a_2b_2c_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Alexander said you have to give me the two sets of bones you know the whereabouts of. Could you do that now, please?" linkto "Mich_7_1"  notes "This node is only visible if the variable Mich_Alex_Force>0 AND Mich_Shovel<1."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I've managed to find a shovel. Could you show me where to dig for the bones of the last two Explorers?" linkto "Mich_6_4a_1"  notes "This option only appears IF the PC has a shovel AND Mich_Shovel>0 AND Mich_Cemetary_Bones=0. Also, the variable Mich_Alex_Force must be greater than 0, OR Mich_G_Counter_Return must be greater than 0 AND Mich_Site_Bones_Return must be greater than 2."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Would you like to come to Crossroads to preside over the burial of the Explorers' bones?" linkto "Mich_8a_1"  notes "This option only appears if the variable Mich_Site_Bones_Return=3 AND Mich_Cemetary_Bones=2 AND the ceremony where the Explorers have buried their dead has NOT already happened. \nIF Mich_G_Counter_Return<=0, go to Mich_8b_1 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Actually, I think we covered everything I need to know. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
