          int=4 linkflags skill_check Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How can you live with the knowledge of the crimes you are responsible for?" linkto "SkillCheck_0_Mich_B_2"  notes "Wrong response for the suicide condition. The weaker of the two guilt trips. It gives Michael the chance to justify himself. Penalty is another node with a speech check to go through.\nModerate speech check. If failed, go to Mich_B_9_1 instead."
          int=4 linkflags skill_check Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No wonder you hide your face behind those robes. I would too, if I had the blood of five innocents on my hands." linkto "SkillCheck_1_Mich_B_2"  notes "Correct response for the suicide condition. Straight for the jugular.\nModerate speech check. If failed, go to Mich_B_9_1 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "It's not for me to judge you or why you want the geiger counter. Is there anything else you want found?" linkto "Mich_5_7_4a_1"  notes ""
